metadata.title: Altdeutsches Liederbuch
metadata.description: A collection of 309 folk songs collected by Franz Magnus Böhme and  later digitized by Helmut Schaffrath.

issues.title: Missing page numbers
issues.description: There are no page numbers in the source files. We do have song numbers, which can be derived from the catalogue numbers.

issues.title: Cannot find scans
issues.description: I can't find any scans of the book to verify the song numbering...

issues.title: Ignoring useful comments
issues.description: We now ignore useful comments besides the metadata. For example, in `deut3790`, we find the comment "Neuere Melodie, noch 1850 am Niederrhein gehoert."
